Description: Removing the need to make good after passing a pipe through a wall, the Linthwaite 110mm PipeSnug is a patented product designed to create a professional finish in seconds. Made of polypropylene and TPE with a black finish, PipeSnug can be used internally or externally and makes a gap completely airtight, helping installers to comply with the latest requirements for Part L of Building Regulations. Supplied in a pack of two, this PipeSnug is suitable for any standard 40mm (1 1/2") solvent-weld waste pipe fitting and 52mm core-drilled hole.
